11:11.337 --> 11:13.072 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
How so?

11:13.105 --> 11:14.874 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN SIPHER, Former CIA Officer:
What strikes
me about this which is so
unusual is, this

11:14.907 --> 11:16.375 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
