government
more than you trust the duly
elected government

11:23.783 --> 11:25.551 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that is in power at the time.

11:25.584 --> 11:29.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what's also unusual about
this, I think,
is many of these leaks, as
frustrating as

11:29.789 --> 11:34.627 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
