administration, don't
strike to the heart of the
investigation.

11:34.660 --> 11:40.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This one sounds like it may do
so, because
it highlights a sensitive
collection effort,

11:40.633 --> 11:45.404 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
if, in fact, true, and also it
looks like
it gives some information on
some of the things

11:45.438 --> 11:47.973 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
