edges for months
now.

11:48.007 --> 11:51.343 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Frank Montoya,
turning to
you, what is your reaction to
all this?

11:51.377 --> 11:57.049 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
