to see here,
please move on.

12:00.186 --> 12:01.420 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What is your reaction?

12:01.454 --> 12:03.155 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRANK MONTOYA JR., Former FBI
Official: John
is spot on.

12:03.189 --> 12:08.360 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think some of the other
aspects of this,
we get track two kind of
communications or

12:08.394 --> 12:14.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
