call these,
whether it's a back-channel
access to a government,

12:14.166 --> 12:19.305 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but that's usually when you are
the government
in power, having that
communication with another

12:19.338 --> 12:21.107 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
government.

12:21.140 --> 12:25.644 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What really stands out to me in
this one is
the discussion, if true, as John
noted, about

12:25.678 --> 12:31.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
