13:02.782 --> 13:04.216 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Why is that particularly
troubling?

13:04.250 --> 13:07.219 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN SIPHER: This is a very
sophisticated
adversary.

13:07.253 --> 13:11.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The notion that we would go and
work with
them inside their embassy, this
is something

13:11.857 --> 13:14.460 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
