professionals.

13:14.493 --> 13:20.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it almost is, if you want to
assume this
is naivete by the Trump campaign
and Mr. Kushner,

13:20.933 --> 13:24.737 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
