chosen vehicle

13:51.463 --> 13:52.798 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
for having those conversations?

13:52.832 --> 13:57.770 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN SIPHER: It's possible, but
like Frank
