the secrecy?

14:05.845 --> 14:08.981 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The president-elect had been
talking about
changing the relationship with
Russia for

14:09.014 --> 14:10.783 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
