this effort
to try to hide from your own
government what

14:14.787 --> 14:16.522 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
you're doing.

14:16.555 --> 14:20.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRANK MONTOYA JR.: Yes, if I
could add to
that, William, this is also
demonstrating

14:20.125 --> 14:24.129 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
a gross distrust or mistrust of
his own intelligence
community.

14:24.163 --> 14:27.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If that's what he wanted to do,
we could have
facilitated that for him.

14:27.933 --> 14:33.339 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Even as president-elect, moving
into the inauguration
and beyond, when he becomes the
government,

14:33.372 --> 14:35.541 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
this is what we do for our
presidents.

14:35.574 --> 14:38.978 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: I know you
