14:41.080 --> 14:45.885 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What do these ongoing leaks mean
to them,
do to them, do to their ability
to do their

14:45.918 --> 14:47.686 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
