know what their
government is up to?

15:20.619 --> 15:23.422 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRANK MONTOYA JR.: Yes, that's
one of the
conundrums right now.

15:23.455 --> 15:28.360 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This started out anyway as a
counterintelligence
investigation.

15:28.394 --> 15:30.262 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's become public.

15:30.296 --> 15:32.865 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There are aspects of this, I
think, that are
really important.

15:32.898 --> 15:39.438 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When you look at it from a
historical context,
for instance, one of the key
sources in the

15:39.471 --> 15:42.574 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
