16:05.631 --> 16:07.399 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: John, did you
want to add
to that?

16:07.433 --> 16:09.234 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN SIPHER: Just want to add
