reasons.

32:53.237 --> 32:58.576 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: We're setting up a
task force
in every federal agency to
identify and remove

32:58.609 --> 33:04.482 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
